{"id":662068,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/662068.html","date":"2021-01-27T18:39:31Z","modified":"2021-01-27T18:39:31Z","title":"【404文库】基本常识 | 北京属于农村地区的实锤","content":"<p><strong>三条公开信息</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>国家卫健委规定，春节从低风险地区返回农村地区需要持有7天内核酸阴性证明，并做好14天居家健康监测。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>国家发改委规定，各地在执行就地过年的政策时，不能擅自加码，更不能层层加码。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>北京市规定，春节期间低风险地区人员进京、返京需持7日内核酸阴性证明，抵京后实行14天健康监测。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>逻辑链条</strong></p>\n<p>农村地区需执行【7+14】防疫政策</p>\n<p>且该范围不可扩大，非该范围不得加码</p>\n<p>则执行该政策的都是农村地区</p>\n<p>且执行该政策的仅有农村地区</p>\n<p>而北京全域执行【7+14】政策</p>\n<p><strong>结论：</strong></p>\n<p>北京属于农村地区。</p>\n<p>附证据3条：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_662069\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-662069\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/Screen-Shot-2021-01-27-at-6.30.26-PM-e1611772264258.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"464\" class=\"size-full wp-image-662069\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-662069\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">国家卫健委规定</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_662070\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-662070\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/Screen-Shot-2021-01-27-at-6.31.10-PM-e1611772313846.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"423\" class=\"size-full wp-image-662070\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-662070\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">国家发改委规定<br /></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_662071\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-662071\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/Screen-Shot-2021-01-27-at-6.32.28-PM-e1611772376781.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"379\" class=\"size-full wp-image-662071\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-662071\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">北京市规定</p></div>\n<p><strong>提前驳斥杠精</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>北京有一个中风险区域一个高风险区域，所以应该严管。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>基本常识驳斥：</strong>来自低风险地区的民众不嫌弃你北京，你还嫌弃起人家了？而且发改委的规定里也说了不能一刀切，北京的中高风险区域一个在大兴一个在顺义，就算严格执行也不需要北京全域。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>北京是首都，情况复杂，单独出规定可以理解。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>基本常识驳斥：</strong>返乡人员需要执行【7+14】政策的一大理由是说农村地区医疗条件薄弱，防控能力差。请问，全国还有比北京医疗条件更好，防控能力更强的地方？说到底还是北京作为农村地区服务民众的意识不强嘛。不接受反驳。</p>\n<p>相关阅读：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_662072\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-662072\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/FireShot-Capture-175-北京属于农村地区的实锤-mp.weixin.qq_.com_-e1611772441243.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1041\" class=\"size-full wp-image-662072\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-662072\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">相关阅读</p></div>\n","author":1061,"categories":[18271,41492,38912,38985],"tags":[42745,40940,40890,39920,9605,42728]}